ed="T" n="0807c12"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0807c12"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000010127"><placeName>吳郡</placeName><placeName>破山寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011543">常達</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0807c13"/><persName key="A011543">釋常達</persName>，字<persName key="A011543">文舉</persName>，俗姓<name>顧</name>，<placeName key="PL000000010157">海隅</placeName>人也。發跡<placeName key="PL000000058011"><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>何</sic><corr>河</corr></choice><lb
ed="T" n="0807c14"/>陽</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000058013">大福山</placeName>，遊學<placeName key="PL000000015039">江淮</placeName>諸勝寺。<persName key="A011543">達</persName>允迪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g786"/>中和，<lb
ed="T" n="0807c15"/>克完戒法，專講<persName key="A001519">南山</persName>律鈔<ptr target="#n1290"/>。後求《涅槃》圓音，<lb
ed="T" n="0807c16"/>《法華》止觀<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g187"/>，復通《陰符》<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n1856"/>、《老》、《莊》、百家之書，其餘分<lb
ed="T" n="0807c17"/>時之學，盡<ref type="person" target="#A002704 #A023364">二王</ref>之筆迹。後隨方參禪，詣于<lb
ed="T" n="0807c18"/>宗極<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1380"/>。俄屬<persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>滅法，歎曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A011543">我</ref>生不辰，不自<lb
ed="T" n="0807c19"/><ref type="person" target="#A011543">我</ref>後<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1340"/>！」由是寢默山棲，委裘遁世而無悶焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0807c20"/><persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>重建法幢，荐興精舍。合境民人皆<persName key="A011543">達</persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0807c21"/>化導，故<anchor xml:id="beg0807005"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0807005"/>守<persName key="A011551">韋曙</persName>特加崇重。身不衣繒纊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g791"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0807c22"/>室唯蒙薜蘿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g795"/>，四眾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/>知歸，諸方慕化，其潔白<lb
ed="T" n="0807c23"/>鶴鷺如也。<date from-iso="+0871-01-29" key="j20392152039598" to-iso="+0872-02-16"><name>咸通</name>十二年</date>，合郭僧民請紹四眾<lb
ed="T" n="0807c24"/>教誨。或遊遨坰牧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g797"/>，或<anchor xml:id="beg0807sgsz11"/>嘯<anchor xml:id="end0807sgsz11"/>傲海壖<ptr type="glossary" target="#g253"/>，不出林麓<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g806"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0807c25"/>動<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g807"/>經數載。雖貴士單車詣門，莫得而見。於<lb
ed="T" n="0807c26"/>七五言詩，追用<name>元和</name>之體<ptr type="glossary" target="#g808"/>著《青山履道歌》，<lb
ed="T" n="0807c27"/>播人脣吻。忽於自恣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1221"/>明辰<ptr target="#n1857"/>，鳩眾於長廊，合<lb
ed="T" n="0807c28"/>掌遂申長別，辭甚剛正。因臥疾不起，絕食<lb
ed="T" n="0807c29"/>七日而逝，實<date key="j20405882040588" when-iso="+0874-11-02"><name>咸通</name>十五年九月十六日</date>也，春<pb ed="T" n="0808a" xml:id="T50.2061.0808a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0808a01"/>秋七十四，僧臘五十一。門人<persName key="A011552">會清</persName>、<persName key="A019410">傳郎</persName>奉靈<lb
ed="T" n="0808a02"/>柩殯于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010127">寺</ref>之東南三百步。<date from-iso="+0876-02-03" key="j20410462041399" to-iso="+0877-01-21">後年</date>即墳起塔，<lb
ed="T" n="0808a03"/><placeName key="PL000000024832">頴川</placeName><persName key="A011555">陳言</persName>撰塔銘，邑大夫<placeName key="PL000000026334">汝南</placeName><persName key="A011558">周思輯</persName>為檀<lb
ed="T" n="0808a04"/>信，<date from-iso="+0877-01-22" key="j20414002041783" to-iso="+0878-02-09"><name>乾符</name>四年</date>立碑焉<ptr target="#n1858"/>。</p>
